Text: Broken...a cry...dreams of glory...come to die...♪
Urggghhh! I'll gut any of ye what lays a hand on me muse!
Scurvy dogs... Ye know not love! Aggghhh...
L-Land!? Land ho! Diamanda, I've come...urgh...home...

BURN, BURN!
HM? WHERE IS BURN?

Biggy is big! Biggy is strong!
No one stands up to Biggy!
Biggy has only begun to fight!
Biggy is small, but Biggy's heart is big!

Aieeeeee!
Biggy's too young to die!

YOU KILL MY SON?
I KILL YOU!
Hearken unto me, brave Mogglesguard! These villains shall threaten you no more!
Lend me your strength, and I shall purge our enemies from Thornmarch!
You shall suffer for your transgressions against my subjects!
Hold fast, Mogglesguard! Together we shall cast them out!
Mogglesguard, to arms! Your king has need of you!
Receive of my body, Mogglesguard! Let my strength become yours!
Begone, pomless ones! Torment my subjects no more!
Slake my hunger and know true glory!
I shall feast upon your very soul!

I still hunger...
Bring me more...more!
Your souls are mine at last!
This way lies the first stage! By way of a warm-up, your opponents will be beasts and mammets!
The second stage begins! Gird your loins for a beastly encounter!
You have done well to come this far, but the hardest trials are yet to come. In the third stage, you must clash steel with seasoned gladiators!
And so we arrive at the climactic ending! Victory belongs to the beauteous!
You may be able to stand with the best of the bloodsands, but how will you fare against the mightiest thaumaturge of the age?
There is no escaping the Absolute Bind!
Run, my pretties, lest you feel the searing kiss of my magicks!
You trespass upon my domain, tainted of the Light!
Drink deep of the sea's bitter draught!
Mine is the power to cleanse all things! Naught can withstand the relentless onslaught of my waves!
You challenge me with trickery? Fools! Your mortal contrivances cannot quell the raging sea!
My waters...are stilled... This...this is the blessing of Light?
Your flesh shall feed my minions of the deep!
Knowings of cheesemake is gobbie secret!
All cheese recipes are belong to Illuminati!
Shkoh! Target is eyecatched! All hands, forcetake Brayflox!
Illuminati brainfruit is frontmost! Uplanders have no chance to survive!
Who dares set foot within my domain? The wretched white mages of Amdapor?
To face me is to face thy deepest, darkest nightmares!
Not even in eternal sleep shalt thou be free from the terror of my weaving!

来たな冒険者、お前に勝って武器をいただくぜ！
ゆくぞ、エンキドゥ！　我が心の友よ！
Is just too much for me...
Ehhh!? Why, I've been had! This is far from the strongest of spears! I feel so betrayed!
Goodness gracious! I, uh, just remembered something!
Go on, Enkidu! It's toad─your favorite!
I must say, I quite enjoy these tussles. I feel we've gained an understanding─
An understanding that I will pound you silly! Ha ha!
Urgh! I won't go down so easily!

これなるはエオルゼアいちの強者……
その名も、剣豪ギルガメッシュ！
Obtain the main storage vault key

Man the cannon whilst
we bleed the beast!

...D-Down to the last man?
We have failed...

Thou art brave, Bringer of Light.
Yet bravery alone shall not convince me of thy worth!
Prove thy words are more than empty banter!

This battle shall decide thy fate.
Canst thou weather mine awakened ire!?

Thy judgment is nigh...
To me, mine arbiters!

Art thou truly of man?
Thy strength exceeds mine expectations...

I pronounce thy sentence!
By the radiance of eld be thee judged!
You think me an aberration, do you!? Denials are futile─I can smell your vile thoughts!
You shall pay dearly for making mock of my appearance!
Scorch their insolent hides, my hounds!
The hounds...grow silent... Finally...I may rest...
You who would bare steel against the emperor. You shall not pass so long as I draw breath!

Activating support protocol...
Charging energy stores!
Ignorant savages! You will rue the day you set foot within this tower!

Energy stores replenished...
In the name of Emperor Xande, I shall annihilate you!

Activating defense protocol...
Be it steel or sorcery, your weapons shall not avail you!
My, my, such unruly guests. 'Twould seem a little diversion is in order.
That will do for the opening act. Let the curtains rise for the main attraction!

Inconceivable...
Beware, Your Majesty... Danger approaches...
Mine is the power of darkness! Even the stars must bend to my will!
I shall crush all who dare oppose me!
My defeat...means nothing... Darkness...shall devour all...
Clear the Tomb of King Galvanth the Dominator
Urgh... I told them she was weird...but they wouldn't listen...
I...I can't move my body! Help me!
<huff> <puff> I thought I was done for... I owe you one...
I...I can't stand being here any longer. I'll see you outside!
Thank you ever so much for coming to our wedding! Your body means the world to Avere!
Hm? Where are our witnesses? The ceremony can't begin without them!
Your wait is over, my love! All you have ever dreamed of is right here!
To have and to hold, for better or for worse, for richer or for poorer...
In sickness and in health, to love and to cherish...till death us do part!
Oh, Avere! I can feel the strength of your love inside me!
Nooo... Please don't go... Don't leave me alone...
Slay the vicegerent to the Warden
We got usselves some company, lads! In the name o' Lord Leviathan...kill 'em an' make 'em dead!
Look sharp, ye useless bloody whoresons!
Kill 'em, I said! What part o' that don't ye understand!?
Are we pirates or spineless swivin' jellyfish!? Fight harder!
You! Yer that bastard 'venturer from afore! It's yer fault we're abominations!
Ye want Lord Leviathan to punish us again!? Get yer poxy arses over here, all o' ye!

Ack, sod this...
You lot, take care o' the rest!
I'll be waitin' fer ye with a surprise...assumin' ye live long enough, that is!
H-How the hells did I miss!? That's balls, I tell ye!

Adventurers? Here?
Why lookout no catch you!?
You brave to defy Silverscales─brave or stupid!
Honor to you who slay Koheel Ja!
Much honor in death by old magicks of Mamool Ja!

We smash them, Brother?
Into pulp, yesss, into pulp!

I no hold back, Brother!
Yesss, kill them─kill them now!

Brother, I d-d-die?
Me too, Brothe...

Run, run, run!
None can quench firelit spear!

Brother, they doomed with no heali─
Shhh! Keep tricksy secret to yourself!

Sick ones make sickness, Brother!
Ehehehe, so badly will they ache!
Those who have taken up the sword shall perish by the sword!
Rise to join in the chorus, my brothers!
Embrace the serenity... Renounce the hatreds that consume you...
And scatter them like dust in the wind...
Guests? But you weren't invited! Well, no matter─you shall have a splendid performance all the same!
I had th-thought to play you for fools─but none are more fool than I...
I spy with my giant eye...prey for the hunting!

Round and round the hand does go.
Who will it slaughter? Nobody knows!
N-No, my fate is grown dark before my eye...
In darkness, all is as one. Be it hope or despair, everything is mine to devour.
The light of your world will fade amidst the darkness!
The void shall consume all that is!

You cannot overcome what does not exist!
Of darkness I am born...and to darkness I shall return!
Come, then. Thou shalt be weighed in the balances.
Receive of my breath, and ye shall live once more.
Into thee I place my spirit. Rise, my child, and join in the chorus.
Come forth, children of my children, as a cloud to cover the land.
Hearken to me, mortal, and thou shalt know I am thy lord.
Heh heh heh. So thou art gifted...
Come, then. Thou shalt be weighed in the balances.
Into thee I place my spirit. Rise, my child, and join in the chorus.
I bid thee rise, my child, and join in the chorus once more.
Yet full of fear is thy heart.
Heh heh heh. So thou art gifted...
Hearken to me, mortal, and thou shalt know I am thy lord.
I am undone...but my master's seal is broken!
Argh, oil everywhere! You shall pay dearly, accursed mortals!

I shall not toy with you as does Lahabrea!
Witness the terrible might of a true servant of Zodiark!

Writhing powers of ruination!
From the deepest pits of the abyss I summon thee!

Insatiable hunger of the void!
Devour all light and return this world to perfect darkness!

By Zodiark's name I command thee!
River of time, mire mine enemy in thy sluggish flow!
You shall wither in the merciless embrace of eternity!

But...you are shorn of Her blessing!
How do you yet resist me!?

Impossible!
Has he power over...time itself!?
To my side, Enkidu! The battle is joined!

Owww! It hurts! It hurts!
Enkidu! Your master wants for succor!
Fight on, Enkidu, my ever faithful─hm!?

You'll get no quarter from me this time.
Have at thee!

You have some skill, I'll give you that...
But Gilgamesh has only just begun to fight!

Most impressive!
Very well─I, too, shall fight with all my strength!
No! The mighty Gilgamesh will not be defeated!
Enkidu! Are the bonds of our friendship so fragile!?
We claim victory this day, or Ishgard falls! Accept the Fury into your heart, and defend this bridge with your life's blood!

Slings and arrows shall avail us little against this foe.
Ready the cannons!

They seek to swarm the healers!
Focus your attacks on the dragonflies!
